<title>kl ạlmkẖạwf</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- kl ạlmkẖạwf sẖlthạ lmạ fy
 ḥḍnk sẖltny
 msẖ dy wʿwdk qlthạ? ṣrkẖẗ lyk ạ̉nqdẖtny
 wqt ạlblạyạ wạlmḥn jyt zy rạbʿ fy ạlạ̉twn
 rtẖyt wqlbk ly ḥny ạ̹zạy ạ̉myn zyk ykẖwn
 ạlqrạr- rby bạʿẓm nʿmtk wạ̉htf bfḍlk kl ḥyn
 wạ̉sẖhd brwʿẗ rḥmtk wqt ạltjạrb wạlạ̉nyn
 2- msẖ hạnsy̱ rwʿẗ wqftk lmạ bạ̹ydk kẖdtny
 wlạ hạnsy̱ lḥẓẗ sndtk lmạ tʿbt ḥmltny
 jyt ly bnʿmẗ rfʿtny rgẖm ạltjạrb wạlậlạm
 lmạ ạnḥnyt ṭmnty mạ hw ạ̹nt lyk ậkẖr klạm</lyrics>
</song>